cs.CV, cs.GR, cs.RO, cs.MM, cs.LG. 

The paper addresses the problem of 3D human pose estimation using deep learning and image-based synthesis. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves 3D motion capture data and kinematic constraints, which suggest possible categories such as cs.GR (Graphics) and cs.RO (Robotics). The use of synthetic images and clustering for classification may also indicate categories such as cs.MM (Multimedia) and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
